latestPosts.caption:
Nandi products now available on @bigbasketcom and @letsblinkit .

I choose Nandi products for tasty and healthy experience for me and my family . Now it’s ur turn and try out healthy burger recipes with @nandi.foods 

Healthy burger recipe:- So sabse pehle we will take Nandi ki suji jisme we added curd, water,salt and 1tesp of soda. Mix it well and steam it in the idli maker for 10-15 mins. Now to make the masala, add mustard seeds, curry leaves chopped chilli, onion boiled potato, fir we added Nandi ka haldi, powder,red chilli powder and meat powder and salt. Now cut the prepared idli into two halves apply green chutney on both sides and slized onion, tomato and potato mixture and toast in a pan.
.
